      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car from day one, and it is in truly pristine condition. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. I'm honestly a little sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be so thrilled with it. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
