    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true time-capsule vehicle. Finished in its original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like gloss, the exterior has been protected by a professional ceramic coating and shows absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin retains that genuine new-car scent; the premium leather seats remain firm with zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, supported by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled environment. From the pristine, dust-free engine bay to the untouched factory floor mats, this vehicle is indistinguishable from the day it first rolled off the showroom floor. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
